The paper discusses a method for visual question answering, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The approach involves dynamically utilizing data from an external source, which involves adapting to new data and learning from it (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of efficient retrieval and cross-domain adaptation, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
